social_posts.post_text: So long Chile 🇨🇱 What a wild 2 weeks!

Big Sky Winter Ball Year 2! The @406agave Red carpet was rock in’ !Nearly $20,000 raised for the @bigskyhousingtrust !! Incredible night with our incredible community. Looking forward to next year!

Thank you @bozefoto for the photos, @theindybigsky for hosting, the @zarembapottsgroup for putting it all together and to @bigskyhousingtrust for all they do for our town🙏🏽
Not a goodbye but a see you later… Ruth & Marty are off to Nashville. Love y’all, we are so excited for your next journey!! Can’t wait to visit! ❤️
What a fun night with fantastic lookin people! #406agavecrew #bigskybravery #fightnight #lukesshoes
